{
  "id": "adv_card_skr_09_01",
  "title": "川咲さくら 1話 川咲さくら流銀河一のお嫁さん",
  "script": [
    {
      "type": "background",
      "src": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/storyBackground/env_adv_2d_office-01-noon.webp",
      "bgName": "env_adv_3d_office-01-000-noon",
      "startTime": 0
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "skr",
      "speakerName": "川咲さくら",
      "speakerNameEn": "Sakura",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-sakura.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/cardStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_card_skr_09_01/sud_vo_adv_card_skr_09_01-skr001.m4a",
      "text": "ウエディングをテーマにしたグラビアですか？",
      "translations": {
        "en": "A wedding-themed gravure shoot?",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 0.8,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "koh",
      "speakerName": "{user}",
      "speakerNameEn": "{user}",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-makino.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/cardStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_card_skr_09_01/sud_vo_adv_card_skr_09_01-koh001.m4a",
      "text": "そうなんだ\n雑誌の企画で使うグラビアを撮影したいらしい",
      "translations": {
        "en": "That's right.\nThey want to shoot a gravure for a magazine feature.",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 5.9333333333,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "koh",
      "speakerName": "{user}",
      "speakerNameEn": "{user}",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-makino.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/cardStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_card_skr_09_01/sud_vo_adv_card_skr_09_01-koh002.m4a",
      "text": "アイドルとの新婚生活の様子を\nいろんなシチュエーションで撮影するらしいぞ",
      "translations": {
        "en": "They're going to shoot various situations\nportraying newlywed life with an idol.",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 11.9,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "skr",
      "speakerName": "川咲さくら",
      "speakerNameEn": "Sakura",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-sakura.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/cardStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_card_skr_09_01/sud_vo_adv_card_skr_09_01-skr002.m4a",
      "text": "憧れのアイドルとの結婚生活なんて\n凄く魅力的ですね！",
      "translations": {
        "en": "Newlywed life with your favorite idol…\nThat sounds so appealing!",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 18.0666666667,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "skr",
      "speakerName": "川咲さくら",
      "speakerNameEn": "Sakura",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-sakura.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/cardStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_card_skr_09_01/sud_vo_adv_card_skr_09_01-skr003.m4a",
      "text": "千紗ちゃんだったら毎朝優しく起こしてくれそうかも\nほのぼのした家庭になりそうですね",
      "translations": {
        "en": "I bet Chisa-chan would wake me up gently every morning.\nIt would be such a peaceful home.",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 25.2666666667,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "skr",
      "speakerName": "川咲さくら",
      "speakerNameEn": "Sakura",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-sakura.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/cardStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_card_skr_09_01/sud_vo_adv_card_skr_09_01-skr004.m4a",
      "text": "雫ちゃんだったらどうなるかなぁ\nむしろ「アイドルと結婚したい」って言ったりして",
      "translations": {
        "en": "I wonder what it would be like with Shizuku-chan.\nShe might even say‚ “I want to marry an idol!”",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 31.8,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "skr",
      "speakerName": "川咲さくら",
      "speakerNameEn": "Sakura",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-sakura.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/cardStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_card_skr_09_01/sud_vo_adv_card_skr_09_01-skr005.m4a",
      "text": "遙子ちゃんは私がドジなことをしても\nフォローしてくれそうです！",
      "translations": {
        "en": "Haruko-chan would probably cover\nfor me even if I made a mistake!",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 39.8333333333,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "skr",
      "speakerName": "川咲さくら",
      "speakerNameEn": "Sakura",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-sakura.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/cardStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_card_skr_09_01/sud_vo_adv_card_skr_09_01-skr006.m4a",
      "text": "例えば、お弁当を忘れた時とか\n現場まで持って来てくれたり……",
      "translations": {
        "en": "Like‚ if I forgot my lunch‚\nshe’d bring it to me…",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 45.3666684468,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "skr",
      "speakerName": "川咲さくら",
      "speakerNameEn": "Sakura",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-sakura.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/cardStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_card_skr_09_01/sud_vo_adv_card_skr_09_01-skr007.m4a",
      "text": "みんな魅力的なお嫁さんになりそうですよね～\n想像するだけでキュンキュンしちゃいます！",
      "translations": {
        "en": "Everyone would make such charming brides~.\nJust thinking about it makes my heart flutter!",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 52.5000017802,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "koh",
      "speakerName": "{user}",
      "speakerNameEn": "{user}",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-makino.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/cardStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_card_skr_09_01/sud_vo_adv_card_skr_09_01-koh003.m4a",
      "text": "サニピのみんなの想像をしているところ悪いが\n今回はさくらが指名されているんだ",
      "translations": {
        "en": "It’s nice that you’re imagining all the members of Sunny Peace‚\nbut this time‚ Sakura‚ you're the one they chose.",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 59.5000017802,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "skr",
      "speakerName": "川咲さくら",
      "speakerNameEn": "Sakura",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-sakura.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/cardStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_card_skr_09_01/sud_vo_adv_card_skr_09_01-skr008.m4a",
      "text": "へぇ～、なるほど～。私が……\nえぇ！？　わ、私が指名されてるんですか！？",
      "translations": {
        "en": "Oh~ I see. Me…\nWhat?! I-I’m the one they chose?!",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 67.6333351135,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "koh",
      "speakerName": "{user}",
      "speakerNameEn": "{user}",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-makino.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/cardStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_card_skr_09_01/sud_vo_adv_card_skr_09_01-koh004.m4a",
      "text": "ああ。「明るい家庭を築くことが出来そう」\nという理由で、ぜひさくらに受けてほしいと先方がな",
      "translations": {
        "en": "Yeah. They believe you can create a bright and cheerful home.\nSo‚ they would love for you to accept the offer.",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 75.8000017802,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "skr",
      "speakerName": "川咲さくら",
      "speakerNameEn": "Sakura",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-sakura.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/cardStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_card_skr_09_01/sud_vo_adv_card_skr_09_01-skr009.m4a",
      "text": "明るいだなんて……えへへへ～",
      "translations": {
        "en": "Cheerful… ehehe.",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 80.2190924167,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "koh",
      "speakerName": "{user}",
      "speakerNameEn": "{user}",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-makino.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/cardStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_card_skr_09_01/sud_vo_adv_card_skr_09_01-koh005.m4a",
      "text": "今までにない新たな挑戦になると思うが\n受けてくれるか？",
      "translations": {
        "en": "I think this will be a new challenge you’ve never faced before.\nWill you accept it?",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 88.6666684468,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "skr",
      "speakerName": "川咲さくら",
      "speakerNameEn": "Sakura",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-sakura.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/cardStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_card_skr_09_01/sud_vo_adv_card_skr_09_01-skr010.m4a",
      "text": "もちろん受けさせていただきます！\n私も興味がわいてきました！",
      "translations": {
        "en": "Of course I’ll accept!\nI’m interested now!",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 93.1666684468,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "koh",
      "speakerName": "{user}",
      "speakerNameEn": "{user}",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-makino.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/cardStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_card_skr_09_01/sud_vo_adv_card_skr_09_01-koh006.m4a",
      "text": "それは良かった。ちなみに、撮影には\nウエディングドレスを着たシーンもあるみたいだ",
      "translations": {
        "en": "That’s good. By the way‚ it seems like there’s\na scene where you’ll be wearing a wedding dress.",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 99.2333351135,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "skr",
      "speakerName": "川咲さくら",
      "speakerNameEn": "Sakura",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-sakura.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/cardStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_card_skr_09_01/sud_vo_adv_card_skr_09_01-skr011.m4a",
      "text": "本当ですか！？　琴乃ちゃん達が着ているのを見て\n私も着てみたいなーって思ってたんです！",
      "translations": {
        "en": "Really?! I saw Kotono-chan and the others wearing them‚\nand I thought I’d like to try one on!",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 106.0666684468,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "koh",
      "speakerName": "{user}",
      "speakerNameEn": "{user}",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-makino.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/cardStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_card_skr_09_01/sud_vo_adv_card_skr_09_01-koh007.m4a",
      "text": "さくらとの結婚生活がどうなるのか\nファンに伝えられるようにしないとな",
      "translations": {
        "en": "You need to show the fans what\nnewlywed life with Sakura would be like.",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 112.3666684468,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "skr",
      "speakerName": "川咲さくら",
      "speakerNameEn": "Sakura",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-sakura.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/cardStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_card_skr_09_01/sud_vo_adv_card_skr_09_01-skr012.m4a",
      "text": "はい！　ファンのみなさんに世界一幸せな\n結婚生活をお届け出来るように頑張ります！",
      "translations": {
        "en": "Yes! I’ll do my best to show the fans\nthe happiest newlywed life in the world!",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 119.0000017802,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "koh",
      "speakerName": "{user}",
      "speakerNameEn": "{user}",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-makino.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/cardStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_card_skr_09_01/sud_vo_adv_card_skr_09_01-koh008.m4a",
      "text": "あまりハードルを上げ過ぎないようにな",
      "translations": {
        "en": "Try not to raise their expectations too high.",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 122.6909293175,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "skr",
      "speakerName": "川咲さくら",
      "speakerNameEn": "Sakura",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-sakura.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/cardStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_card_skr_09_01/sud_vo_adv_card_skr_09_01-skr013.m4a",
      "text": "ただ、今の私だと、想いに応えられるかちょっと不安\nです。結婚生活の知識なんて全然ありませんから",
      "translations": {
        "en": "However‚ I’m a little worried whether I can live up to those\nexpectations. I don’t know anything about newlywed life.",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 130.7666684468,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "koh",
      "speakerName": "{user}",
      "speakerNameEn": "{user}",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-makino.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/cardStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_card_skr_09_01/sud_vo_adv_card_skr_09_01-koh009.m4a",
      "text": "まぁ、アイドル活動で忙しいし\nそもそもそういう歳でもないからな",
      "translations": {
        "en": "Well‚ you’re busy with idol activities‚\nand you’re not old enough for that anyway.",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 140.1000017802,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "skr",
      "speakerName": "川咲さくら",
      "speakerNameEn": "Sakura",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-sakura.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/cardStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_card_skr_09_01/sud_vo_adv_card_skr_09_01-skr014.m4a",
      "text": "{user}さんは\n詳しかったりするんですか？",
      "translations": {
        "en": "Do you happen to\nknow a lot about it‚ {user}-san?",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 144.561047791,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "koh",
      "speakerName": "{user}",
      "speakerNameEn": "{user}",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-makino.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/cardStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_card_skr_09_01/sud_vo_adv_card_skr_09_01-koh010.m4a",
      "text": "俺も大して詳しくはないよ\n漫画やドラマで得た知識があるぐらいだな",
      "translations": {
        "en": "I’m not really that knowledgeable about it either.\nI only know what I’ve learned from manga and dramas.",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 149.5000017802,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "skr",
      "speakerName": "川咲さくら",
      "speakerNameEn": "Sakura",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-sakura.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/cardStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_card_skr_09_01/sud_vo_adv_card_skr_09_01-skr015.m4a",
      "text": "なるほど～……せっかくの指名ですし\nやるからにはちゃんと準備していきたいですね",
      "translations": {
        "en": "I see~. …Since I’ve been chosen for this‚\nI want to prepare for it properly.",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 157.0666684468,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "skr",
      "speakerName": "川咲さくら",
      "speakerNameEn": "Sakura",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-sakura.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/cardStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_card_skr_09_01/sud_vo_adv_card_skr_09_01-skr016.m4a",
      "text": "最強の妻を目指すつもりでやりたいですが……\nまずは何からすればいいでしょう？",
      "translations": {
        "en": "I want to aim to become the best wife…\nBut what should I do first?",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 165.382684633,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "skr",
      "speakerName": "川咲さくら",
      "speakerNameEn": "Sakura",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-sakura.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/cardStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_card_skr_09_01/sud_vo_adv_card_skr_09_01-skr017.m4a",
      "text": "お母さんには話を聞くとして\nサニピのみんなにもインタビューを……",
      "translations": {
        "en": "I’ll talk to my mom‚\nand… interview the other members of Sunny Peace…",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 172.5666684468,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "koh",
      "speakerName": "{user}",
      "speakerNameEn": "{user}",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-makino.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/cardStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_card_skr_09_01/sud_vo_adv_card_skr_09_01-koh011.m4a",
      "text": "結婚関連の雑誌を読んでみるのもいいかもな\nあとは……恋愛漫画やドラマを見てみるとか？",
      "translations": {
        "en": "Maybe you could try reading some magazines about marriage.\nAnd… watching some romance manga or dramas?",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 179.1333351135,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "koh",
      "speakerName": "{user}",
      "speakerNameEn": "{user}",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-makino.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/cardStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_card_skr_09_01/sud_vo_adv_card_skr_09_01-koh012.m4a",
      "text": "教材があるのとないのとじゃ\n入る知識の量が段違いだからな",
      "translations": {
        "en": "Having reference material makes a world of difference\nin how much knowledge you can gain.",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 185.0666666667,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "skr",
      "speakerName": "川咲さくら",
      "speakerNameEn": "Sakura",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-sakura.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/cardStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_card_skr_09_01/sud_vo_adv_card_skr_09_01-skr018.m4a",
      "text": "なんだか試験勉強みたいですね……\nうぅ、でも私、頑張ってみます！",
      "translations": {
        "en": "It feels like I’m studying for an exam…\nUgh‚ but I’ll try my best!",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 191.8000017802,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "skr",
      "speakerName": "川咲さくら",
      "speakerNameEn": "Sakura",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-sakura.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/cardStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_card_skr_09_01/sud_vo_adv_card_skr_09_01-skr019.m4a",
      "text": "ファンのみなさんや、お仕事をくれた先方の方々に\n喜んでもらうためにも、手は抜けませんから！",
      "translations": {
        "en": "I can’t slack off‚ for the sake of the fans and\nthe people who gave me this opportunity!",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 201.2768895843,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "skr",
      "speakerName": "川咲さくら",
      "speakerNameEn": "Sakura",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-sakura.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/cardStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_card_skr_09_01/sud_vo_adv_card_skr_09_01-skr020.m4a",
      "text": "猛勉強してくるので、ちょっとだけ時間を下さい\n三日ほど、いいでしょうか？",
      "translations": {
        "en": "I’ll go and study hard‚ so give me a little time.\nThree days‚ would that be enough?",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 209.8666745503,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "koh",
      "speakerName": "{user}",
      "speakerNameEn": "{user}",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-makino.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/cardStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_card_skr_09_01/sud_vo_adv_card_skr_09_01-koh013.m4a",
      "text": "ああ、それぐらいなら大丈夫だと思う\n俺もそれを前提にスケジュールを組んでおくよ",
      "translations": {
        "en": "Yeah‚ I think that should be enough.\nI’ll adjust the schedule accordingly.",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 215.933341217,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "skr",
      "speakerName": "川咲さくら",
      "speakerNameEn": "Sakura",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-sakura.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/cardStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_card_skr_09_01/sud_vo_adv_card_skr_09_01-skr021.m4a",
      "text": "ありがとうございます！\nよーっし！　銀河一のお嫁さんを目指しますよ！",
      "translations": {
        "en": "Thank you!\nAlright~! I’m going to aim to be the best bride in the galaxy!",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 221.0666745503,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "koh",
      "speakerName": "{user}",
      "speakerNameEn": "{user}",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-makino.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/cardStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_card_skr_09_01/sud_vo_adv_card_skr_09_01-koh014.m4a",
      "text": "さっきよりもハードルが上がっていないか？",
      "translations": {
        "en": "Are you raising the bar even higher than before?",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 226.3429668267,
      "sfxList": []
